---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';

const serviceSchema = {
  "@type": "Service",
  "@id": "https://lvappraisalco.com/tax-appeal-appraisals#service",
  "name": "Property Tax Appeal Appraisals in Las Vegas",
  "description": "Independent residential appraisals for Clark County property tax appeals, plus ANSI-compliant floor plan sketches and GLA calculations.",
  "provider": { "@id": "https://lvappraisalco.com/#business" },
  "areaServed": { "@type": "AdministrativeArea", "name": "Clark County, Nevada" },
  "serviceType": "Property Tax Appeal Appraisal"
};
---

<Base
  title="Property Tax Appeal Appraisals in Las Vegas | Clark County | Las Vegas Appraisal Co."
  description="Independent appraisals for Clark County property tax appeals, plus ANSI-compliant GLA and floor plan documentation. Call (702) 894-9279."
  canonical="https://lvappraisalco.com/tax-appeal-appraisals"
  schema={serviceSchema}
>

  <div class="service-page-header">
    <div class="narrow">
      <p class="eyebrow">Tax Appeal Appraisals</p>
      <h1>Property Tax Appeal Appraisals in Las Vegas</h1>
      <p style="color: var(--text-secondary); margin-top: 16px; font-size: 1.05rem;">
        Independent evidence of value for your Clark County property tax appeal.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <section>
    <div class="service-content">
      <p>If you believe your Clark County property tax assessment overstates your home's value, an independent appraisal is the strongest evidence you can bring before the Board of Equalization. We provide accurate, well-documented reports that reflect your property's true market value as of the relevant assessment date.</p>

      <h2>What's Included</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Full interior and exterior property inspection</li>
        <li>ANSI-compliant floor plan sketch and gross living area (GLA) calculation</li>
        <li>Comparable sales analysis specific to your neighborhood and assessment period</li>
        <li>A clear, documented report suitable for submission to the Clark County Board of Equalization</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Home Measurement & GLA Verification</h2>
      <p>Assessor records are sometimes wrong — an incorrect square footage figure can inflate your assessed value on its own. We independently measure your home to ANSI Z765 standards and identify discrepancies between your assessor record and actual GLA.</p>

      <h2>Who This Is For</h2>
      <p>Homeowners appealing an assessment, property owners requesting a reassessment after damage or renovation, and attorneys or accountants who need an independent valuation to support a client's appeal.</p>

      <div class="service-cta">
        <p>Get an independent appraisal for your tax appeal.</p>
        <div style="display: flex; gap: 12px; justify-content: center; flex-wrap: wrap;">
          <a href="tel:+17028949279" class="btn btn-primary">(702) 894-9279</a>
          <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-secondary">Request a Quote</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</Base>
